{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.1","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:1","prev_osis_id":"Heb.002.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">J\u00e9sus est sup\u00e9rieur \u00e0 Mo\u00efse. Ne pas imiter l\u2019endurcissement et l\u2019incr\u00e9dulit\u00e9 des anciens Isra\u00e9lites, mais entrer dans le repos de Dieu<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-6: cf. (No 12:7. De 4:5.) (H\u00e9 1:2. Mt 21:33-38.) Za 6:12, 13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi, fr\u00e8res saints, qui avez part \u00e0 la vocation c\u00e9leste, consid\u00e9rez l\u2019ap\u00f4tre et le souverain sacrificateur de la foi que nous professons,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.2.18","name":"H\u00e9breux 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.2.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.2","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:2","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>J\u00e9sus, qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 fid\u00e8le \u00e0 celui qui l\u2019a \u00e9tabli, comme le fut Mo\u00efse dans toute sa maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.1","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.3","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:3","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Car il a \u00e9t\u00e9 jug\u00e9 digne d\u2019une gloire d\u2019autant sup\u00e9rieure \u00e0 celle de Mo\u00efse que celui qui a construit une maison a plus d\u2019honneur que la maison m\u00eame.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.4","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.2","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.4","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:4","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Chaque maison est construite par quelqu\u2019un, mais celui qui a construit toutes choses, c\u2019est Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.5","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:5","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Pour Mo\u00efse, il a \u00e9t\u00e9 fid\u00e8le dans toute la maison de Dieu, comme serviteur, pour rendre t\u00e9moignage de ce qui devait \u00eatre annonc\u00e9;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.6","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.4","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.6","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:6","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>mais Christ l\u2019est comme Fils sur sa maison; et sa maison, c\u2019est nous, pourvu que nous retenions jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la fin la ferme confiance et l\u2019esp\u00e9rance dont nous nous glorifions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.5","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.7","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:7","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.008,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 7-19: cf. Ps 95:8-11. (No 14. Ps 78. 1 Co 10:1-12.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi, selon ce que dit le Saint-Esprit:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Aujourd\u2019hui, si vous entendez sa voix,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.8","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.6","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.8","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:8","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>N\u2019endurcissez pas vos c\u0153urs, comme lors de la r\u00e9volte,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Le jour de la tentation dans le d\u00e9sert,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.9","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.7","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.9","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:9","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>O\u00f9 vos p\u00e8res me tent\u00e8rent<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Pour m\u2019\u00e9prouver, et ils virent mes \u0153uvres<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Pendant quarante ans.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.8","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.10","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:10","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Aussi je fus irrit\u00e9 contre cette g\u00e9n\u00e9ration, et je dis:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils ont toujours un c\u0153ur qui s\u2019\u00e9gare.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils n\u2019ont pas connu mes voies.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.11","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.9","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.11","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:11","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>\n    Je jurai donc dans ma col\u00e8re:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ils n\u2019entreront pas dans mon repos!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.10","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.12","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:12","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Prenez garde, fr\u00e8res, que quelqu\u2019un de vous n\u2019ait un c\u0153ur mauvais et incr\u00e9dule, au point de se d\u00e9tourner du Dieu vivant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.13","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.11","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.13","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:13","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Mais exhortez-vous les uns les autres chaque jour, aussi longtemps qu\u2019on peut dire: Aujourd\u2019hui! Afin qu\u2019aucun de vous ne s\u2019endurcisse par la s\u00e9duction du p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.14","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.12","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.14","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:14","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Car nous sommes devenus participants de Christ, pourvu que nous retenions fermement jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la fin l\u2019assurance que nous avions au commencement,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.15","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.13","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.15","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:15","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>pendant qu\u2019il est dit:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Aujourd\u2019hui, si vous entendez sa voix,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">N\u2019endurcissez pas vos c\u0153urs, comme lors de la r\u00e9volte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.16","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.14","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.16","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:16","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Qui furent, en effet, ceux qui se r\u00e9volt\u00e8rent apr\u00e8s l\u2019avoir entendue, sinon tous ceux qui \u00e9taient sortis d\u2019\u00c9gypte sous la conduite de Mo\u00efse?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.17","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.15","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.17","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:17","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Et contre qui Dieu fut-il irrit\u00e9 pendant quarante ans, sinon contre ceux qui p\u00e9chaient, et dont les cadavres tomb\u00e8rent dans le d\u00e9sert?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.18","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.16","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.18","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:18","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.003.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et \u00e0 qui jura-t-il qu\u2019ils n\u2019entreraient pas dans son repos, sinon \u00e0 ceux qui avaient d\u00e9sob\u00e9i?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.19","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:19","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.17","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.19","label":"","reference":"H\u00e9breux 3:19","prev_osis_id":"Heb.003.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Heb.004.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Heb.3.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Aussi voyons-nous qu\u2019ils ne purent y entrer \u00e0 cause de leur incr\u00e9dulit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Heb.3","name":"H\u00e9breux 3","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.4.1","name":"H\u00e9breux 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.4.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Heb.3.18","name":"H\u00e9breux 3:18","id":"fra-LSG:Heb.3.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc7a6d108.83399294');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc7a6d108.83399294\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc7a6d108.83399294","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefi